#

Tofu Soup

25 min
$8
200 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Main

Tags:

QuickHealthyComfort Food

Description

A warm and comforting tofu soup, perfect for a quick meal packed with flavor and nutrition.

Ingredients

  • firm tofu: 1 block
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • green onions: 2, chopped
  • carrots: 1, sliced
  • spinach: 2 cups
  • sesame oil: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
